@startuml
autonumber
actor "Backoffice Operator" as BO
participant ":System" as System

activate BO
BO -> System : updateAircraftModelSpecs(modelName, fuelCapacity,\n maximumRange, cruisingSpeed)
activate System

note right of System: The system fetches the existing model,\napplies the new valid fields,\nand updates the database.

System --> BO : informs operation success and returns updated model
deactivate System
deactivate BO
@enduml